      { name: 'Catalina Foothills', slug: 'catalina-foothills', lat: 32.3040, lon: -110.9099, description: "The Catalina Foothills at higher elevations see summer temperatures 5-10°F cooler than the valley floor and more dramatic afternoon thunderstorms from the Santa Catalinas." },
