      { name: 'Elmwood Village', slug: 'elmwood-village', lat: 42.9063, lon: -78.8726, description: "Elmwood Village's Victorian tree-lined streets are among Buffalo's best but the famous lake-effect bands hit this neighborhood hard in November-January." },
