    description: "Oklahoma City is at the heart of tornado alley — no major city in America has more tornado history per capita. The city sits on the flat Oklahoma plain with absolutely nothing to impede weather from any direction. The famous Norman Oklahoma National Weather Center (the NWS and NOAA Severe Storms Lab) is here, making this the epicenter of tornado research.",
