    lon: -113.5841,
    timezone: 'America/Denver',
    description: "St. George in southwest Utah's Dixie region is one of America's fastest-growing cities. Its Mojave Desert climate means intense summer heat (regularly over 105°F) but mild winters that make it a major retirement destination. The red rock canyon terrain is stunning but provides little cooling from the desert sun.",
