      { name: 'Snow Canyon', slug: 'snow-canyon-area', lat: 37.1699, lon: -113.6499, description: "Snow Canyon State Park north of St. George has red rock terrain that creates dramatic shade patterns but also intense heat reflection from the canyon walls." },
